name: state-aquatic-management-area-aquisitions
notes: This data layer shows lands acquired by DNR Fisheries through purchase, donation and easement. Some features are hotlinked to scanned deed documents on the DNR Intranet. Use Arcview's hotlink tool to access.

As the trout stream layer is improved, the acquisition layer will be adjusted accordingly. Upstream and downstream boundaries of parcels are accurate. Easement corridors are measured from either the centerline of the stream, or edge of the stream and change with the stream as its course changes over time.
